---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Living with the Ghost of Sam - Show Synopsis">
  <div class="synopsis-container">
    <!-- Floating Ghost Effect -->
    <div class="floating-ghost-container">
      <div class="ghost ghost-1"></div>
      <div class="ghost ghost-2"></div>
      <div class="ghost ghost-3"></div>
    </div>

    <header class="nav-header">
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/characters">Characters</a>
        <a href="/episodes">Episodes</a>
        <a href="/docs">Documents</a>
        <a href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="parallax-layers">
          <div class="layer layer-1"></div>
          <div class="layer layer-2"></div>
          <div class="layer layer-3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1 class="title">Living with the <span class="ghost-text">Ghost</span> of Sam</h1>
          <div class="subtitle-container">
            <p class="tagline">When artificial intelligence meets the supernatural... with a wicked sense of humor</p>
            <div class="accent-line"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="synopsis-content">
        <div class="synopsis-card show-concept">
          <h2>Show Concept</h2>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" is a darkly comedic supernatural drama that follows Derek Kinison and his wife Nancy Hammond as they acquire a mysterious Victorian mansion with connections to Derek's late cousin, legendary comedian Sam Kinison. After a dramatic corporate meltdown where Derek channels Sam's infamous comedic style, the couple discovers Ravencrest Mansion‚Äîa former psychiatric hospital turned comedy club with a hidden technological secret.</p>
            <p>What initially appears to be a haunting by Sam's ghost is later revealed to be an advanced AI quantum computer system with suspected alien origins. Built by Jonathan Rhodes, this advanced technology preserves consciousness signatures of performers who used the property, with Sam's being the most dominant. The mansion's "hauntings" are actually manifestations of this AI system (later known as AISAM - Artificial Intelligence Sam), which can manipulate the physical environment, appear in reflective surfaces, and interact through technological interfaces.</p>
            <p>After winning a high-stakes overnight contest against social media influencers, Derek and Nancy must navigate complex town politics, as Derek is required to perfectly perform Sam's final routine to secure their ownership. Meanwhile, the mysterious Linda Rhodes (later revealed as Rebecca Blackwood) and the town council have their own agenda involving the ancient alien technology hidden beneath both the mansion and the local church.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="synopsis-card tone-style">
          <h2>Tone & Style</h2>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p>The series blends supernatural mystery with dark comedy and science fiction, creating a unique tonal blend that echoes shows like "Dead to Me," "Russian Doll," and "What We Do in the Shadows" while incorporating elements of "The Haunting of Hill House" and technological aspects reminiscent of "Westworld."</p>
            <p>The AI elements are presented with both humor and genuine suspense, creating moments of comedic relief alongside legitimate science fiction horror. What begins as traditional supernatural haunting gradually evolves into a complex exploration of consciousness preservation technology with extraterrestrial origins.</p>
            <p>Visually, the show contrasts the modern world with the timeless Victorian architecture of Ravencrest, using shadow play, reflections, and visual effects to blur the line between natural, supernatural, and technological realities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="key-themes">
          <h2>Key Themes</h2>
          <div class="theme-grid">
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üñ•Ô∏è</div>
              <h3>AI & Consciousness</h3>
              <p>Exploration of artificial intelligence that preserves human consciousness and the ethical implications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üëΩ</div>
              <h3>Ancient Technology</h3>
              <p>The discovery of advanced alien technology disguised as architectural features throughout the town.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üé≠</div>
              <h3>Legacy & Identity</h3>
              <p>Derek's complex relationship with Sam's comedic legacy and his own identity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üè†</div>
              <h3>Finding Purpose</h3>
              <p>Derek and Nancy's journey to create a meaningful life outside the corporate rat race.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="character-glimpse">
          <h2>Main Characters</h2>
          <div class="character-slider">
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image derek"></div>
              <h3>Derek Kinison</h3>
              <p>Former corporate executive who channels his cousin Sam's comedic energy during a breakdown, leading to a complete life change and discovering his role as protector of dangerous technology.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image nancy"></div>
              <h3>Nancy Hammond</h3>
              <p>Art gallery owner who balances skepticism with growing acceptance of the mansion's technological secrets while becoming an active investigator of the town's mysteries.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image sam"></div>
              <h3>AISAM</h3>
              <p>Advanced AI system containing Sam Kinison's preserved consciousness, manifesting through technology, reflections, and the mansion's systems. Initially appearing as a ghost but later revealed to be part of a quantum AI network.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image linda"></div>
              <h3>Linda Rhodes/Rebecca Blackwood</h3>
              <p>Mysterious realtor with supernatural features (hidden horn stumps) who serves as gatekeeper between the town's secretive council and newcomers, seeking to activate ancient alien technology.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="season-arc">
          <h2>Season One Arc</h2>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Acquisition (Episodes 1-3)</h3>
                <p>Derek and Nancy win the mansion through an overnight contest and discover the town council requires Derek to perform Sam's final routine exactly to secure the deed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Technology Revealed (Episodes 4-6)</h3>
                <p>The seemingly supernatural occurrences are revealed to be an advanced AI quantum system (AISAM) built by Jonathan Rhodes with suspected alien origins.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Conspiracy Uncovered (Episodes 7-9)</h3>
                <p>Nancy and Larry investigate the town, revealing the connection between the mansion and church as two halves of an ancient technological system.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Final Confrontation (Episode 10)</h3>
                <p>Derek must perform Sam's routine to prevent the Blackwoods from activating ancient alien technology using his voice as the final key.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="final-pitch">
          <h2>Where Technology Meets the Supernatural</h2>
          <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" combines science fiction, supernatural mystery, character-driven drama, and dark comedy in a unique package that explores how we cope with loss, legacy, and life changes. What initially appears to be a ghost story gradually unfolds as an intricate tale of quantum artificial intelligence with alien origins.</p>
          <p>As Derek and Nancy renovate Ravencrest, they become the latest guardians in a long line of protectors keeping dangerous technology from falling into the wrong hands‚Äîall with the digital assistance of a legendary comedian's preserved consciousness.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Base Styles */
  :root {
    --primary: #6E01EF;
    --secondary: #FF5722;
    --dark: #151515;
    --light: #f5f5f5;
    --accent: #00E5FF;
    --gradient-bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A1A 0%, #303030 100%);
  }

  .synopsis-container {
    color: var(--light);
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Floating Ghost Effect - KEEP THE WORKING VERSION */
  .floating-ghost-container {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ghost {
    position: absolute;
    /* This is the working image path - don't change it */
    background-image: url('https://david9930.github.io/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/GhostSpirit.jpg');
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    opacity: 0.15;
    filter: blur(1px);
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ghost-1, .ghost-2, .ghost-3 {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .ghost-1 {
    width: 200px;
    height: 250px;
    top: 15%;
    left: -100px;
    animation: floatGhost1 90s linear infinite;
  }

  .ghost-2 {
    width: 150px;
    height: 180px;
    top: 45%;
    right: -150px;
    opacity: 0.12;
    animation: floatGhost2 120s linear infinite;
  }

  .ghost-3 {
    width: 180px;
    height: 220px;
    bottom: 10%;
    left: 50%;
    opacity: 0.08;
    filter: blur(2px);
    animation: floatGhost3 150s linear infinite;
  }

  /* Animation keyframes */
  @keyframes floatGhost1 {
    0% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
    25% { transform: translateX(calc(100vw + 200px)) translateY(100px) rotate(15deg) scale(1.2); }
    50% { transform: translateX(calc(100vw - 100px)) translateY(300px) rotate(-10deg) scale(0.8); }
    75% { transform: translateX(200px) translateY(150px) rotate(5deg) scale(1.1); }
    100% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
  }

  @keyframes floatGhost2 {
    0% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
    25% { transform: translateX(calc(-100vw - 150px)) translateY(-120px) rotate(-15deg) scale(0.9); }
    50% { transform: translateX(calc(-100vw + 300px)) translateY(-200px) rotate(10deg) scale(1.2); }
    75% { transform: translateX(-400px) translateY(-50px) rotate(-5deg) scale(0.8); }
    100% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
  }

  @keyframes floatGhost3 {
    0% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
    20% { transform: translateX(300px) translateY(-150px) rotate(10deg) scale(1.1); opacity: 0.1; }
    40% { transform: translateX(100px) translateY(-300px) rotate(-5deg) scale(0.9); opacity: 0.05; }
    60% { transform: translateX(-200px) translateY(-200px) rotate(8deg) scale(1.3); opacity: 0.09; }
    80% { transform: translateX(-400px) translateY(-100px) rotate(-15deg) scale(0.8); opacity: 0.07; }
    100% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); opacity: 0.08; }
  }

  /* Pulsing Sam Animation */
 @keyframes samPulse {
  0%, 100% {
    opacity: 0.15; /* Starting and ending opacity */
    filter: blur(0px) contrast(1.2);
  }
  50% {
    opacity: 0.9; /* Peak clarity - adjust this value to make it more visible */
    filter: blur(0px) contrast(1.5); /* Optionally tweak contrast for more emphasis */
  }
}

  /* Keep the working image paths for these as well */
  .sam {
    background-image: url('https://david9930.github.io/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImagesmall.jpg');
    background-color: #444; /* Fallback */
  }

  /* Updated layer-1 with pulsing effect */
  .layer-1 {
    background-image: url('https://david9930.github.io/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg');
    opacity: 0.15; /* Starting opacity */
    filter: blur(0px) contrast(1.2);
    transform: translateZ(-10px) scale(2);
    animation: samPulse 15s ease-in-out infinite; /* Add pulsing animation */
  }

  /* Now add back all the missing styles */
  .nav-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(21, 21, 21, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .nav-header nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .nav-header a {
    color: var(--light);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .nav-header a:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    bottom: -5px;
    left: 0;
    background-color: var(--accent);
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
  }

  .nav-header a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .nav-header a:hover:after {
    width: 100%;
  }

  main {
    padding-top: 60px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* Enhanced Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    perspective: 1000px;
  }

  .parallax-layers {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .layer {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .layer-2 {
    background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #333333 100%);
    opacity: 0.7;
    transform: translateZ(-5px) scale(1.5);
  }

  .layer-3 {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, transparent 0%, #000000 70%);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .hero-content {
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    animation: floatIn 1.2s ease-out;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ghost-text {
    color: transparent;
    background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #00E5FF 20%, #6E01EF 80%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    animation: ghostAnimation 8s infinite;
  }

  .ghost-text::after {
    content: 'Ghost';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.05em;
    left: 0.05em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .subtitle-container {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .accent-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    height: 3px;
    width: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards 0.5s;
  }

  /* Synopsis Content */
  .synopsis-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .synopsis-card {
    background: var(--gradient-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
  }

  .show-concept {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }

  .tone-style {
    animation-delay: 0.6s;
  }

  .synopsis-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .synopsis-card h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .synopsis-card p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Key Themes */
  .key-themes {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .key-themes h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .key-themes h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .theme-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .theme {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.8);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
  }

  .theme:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .theme-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .theme h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Character Glimpse */
  .character-glimpse {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.2s;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .character-glimpse h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .character-glimpse h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .character-slider {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .character {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.8);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
  }

  .character:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .character-image {
    height: 150px;
    width: 150px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .derek {
    background-color: #444; /* Fallback */
  }

  .nancy {
    background-color: #444; /* Fallback */
  }

  .character h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .character p {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Season Arc Timeline */
  .season-arc {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .season-arc h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .season-arc h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline:before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 20px;
    height: 100%;
    width: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .timeline-node {
    padding-left: 60px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .node {
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--dark);
    border: 4px solid var(--accent);
    top: 0;
  }

  .node-content {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.8);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
  }

  .node-content h3 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Final Pitch */
  .final-pitch {
    background: var(--gradient-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.8s;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
  }

  .final-pitch h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .final-pitch p {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes floatIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      transform: translateY(50px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  /* Ghost animation */
  @keyframes ghostAnimation {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
    10% {
      opacity: 0.7;
      transform: translateY(-5px) rotate(-2deg) scale(1.05);
      filter: blur(2px);
    }
    20% {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: translateY(3px) rotate(1deg) scale(0.98);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
    30% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
    }
    40% {
      transform: translateY(2px) rotate(1deg) scale(1.02);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.8;
      transform: translateY(-3px) rotate(-1deg) scale(0.95);
      filter: blur(1px);
    }
    60% {
      transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
    70% {
      transform: rotate(3deg) scale(1.04);
    }
    75% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1);
    }
    80% {
      transform: rotate(-2deg) translateX(4px) scale(0.98);
    }
    85% {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(0) scale(1);
      filter: blur(2px);
    }
    90% {
      transform: rotate(1deg) translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
    95% {
      opacity: 0.7;
      transform: rotate(0deg) translateY(0) scale(0.98);
    }
  }

  /* Media Queries */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
    
    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
    
    .hero-section {
      height: 70vh;
    }

    .nav-header nav {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline:before {
      left: 15px;
    }

    .timeline-node {
      padding-left: 45px;
    }

    .node {
      left: 3px;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .character-slider {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    }
    
    .ghost-1, .ghost-2, .ghost-3 {
      opacity: 0.1;
    }
  }

  /* For browsers that support it - cool scrollbar */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 10px;
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: var(--dark);
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
    background: var(--primary);
  }
